# Self-install footprint (this public repo hosts its own crew). ALL of it is
# machine-specific and would trip scripts/leak-check.sh if committed:
#   .agents/  — this box's config.toml (absolute project_dir) + role prompts
#               that cite the hub event-stream path (/home/…); a stranger
#               cloning shipyard must NOT inherit it. Runners read it from the
#               live checkout via --project, so nightly self-improvement works
#               without it being tracked.
#   .claude/  — installer-created skill symlinks with absolute targets.
#   .worktrees/ — build's scratch checkouts.
.agents/
.claude/
.worktrees/
